import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'
import axios from 'axios'

const promise = axios
  .get('http://localhost:3001/persons')
  .then(response => {
    const notes = response.data
    console.log(notes)
})

ReactDOM.render(
  <App />, 
  document.getElementById('root')
)
